    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1950-12-06T18:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1950-12-06T18:00:00-05:00" n="295"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d295">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">320/12–650: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        United States Representative at the United Nations</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Austin</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">restricted</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1950-12-06T18:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 6, 1950—6 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_Gadel1">Gadel</gloss> 167. For Gerig. Dept authorizes <gloss
                        target="#t_USDel1">USDel</gloss> to join other sponsors in re-submission
                    draft res on <gloss target="#t_SWASWAFR1">SWAfr</gloss> to <gloss
                        target="#t_GA1">GA</gloss>. At dels discretion and <pb facs="0522" n="506"
                        xml:id="pg_506"/> if it considers necessary to obtain approval <gloss
                        target="#t_GA1">GA</gloss>, del is authorized add following para to res:
                    “Authorizes the said comite as a provisional measure also to examine any reports
                    or petitions which may be submitted before the Sixth Session of the <gloss
                        target="#t_GA1">GA</gloss> in accordance with the procedure of the former
                    Mandates System.”<note n="1" xml:id="d295fn1">For text as resubmitted, see <ref
                            target="#pg_507">p. 507</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
